Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.dto

Class IedDTO

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.dto.IedDTO
public class IedDTO extends Object
A representation of the model object IED.

The following features are supported:

  • Ied Name
  • Refers to LDevice
